OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMisty with some fog and drizzle
OL,6,Fslowly lifting, allowing brighter
OL,7,Fspells by the afternoon and feeling
OL,8,Fwarmer. Mist could linger near coasts.
OL,9,FIncreasing chance of showers by Monday
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FTurning drier for a time
OL,13,FMonday evening with variable cloud
OL,14,Famounts. A few showers or some rain
OL,15,Fmight return as cloud increases and
OL,16,Fthickens again overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
