OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTurning breezier Tuesday,
OL,6,Fafter a cloudy morning with showery
OL,7,Frain. Rain dying out and clearing east
OL,8,Fin the afternoon with cloud breaking
OL,9,Fto allow some bright or sunny spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FWednesday, early rain clearing, then
OL,13,Fcolder, brighter with some sunshine.
OL,14,FThursday, windy and bright with
OL,15,Fthickening cloud later. Overnight rain
OL,16,Fclearing Friday morning with sunshine
OL,17,Fand showers. Temperatures near normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
